description:
&lt;p&gt;We have a rare and exciting opportunity for a Telephonist/ Administrator to join us in delivering high quality community mental health care within the South West of Hertfordshire. The vacancy sits within our multi-disciplinary Community Mental Health Team based in Watford serving the needs of people within this diverse locality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an enthusiastic, compassionate and customer focussed person who will have contact via the telephone with people who suffer with severe and enduring mental health problems. We are looking for someone who can maintain a calm, friendly and efficient manner when dealing with service users, their relatives, colleagues and visitors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The area is well served with transport links to historic Hertfordshire and its glorious countryside as well as into London and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameRebecca VukovichJob titleOffice ManagerEmail addressrebecca.vukovich@nhs.netTelephone number07813 404234&lt;/p&gt;
